Hello All,
I was wondering what happened to the list, it's good to see that it is
working again, I purchased gladiator a while ago because it was loads
of fun to play multiplayer, and I support the idea for a maps page.

I would also like to point out that when I last checked the "boost"
program you have available for download it outdated, it modifies the
wrong locations in the file (I mucked around a bit and found some of
the useful Hex locations, but I can't write a replacement program).

I had a list of bugs and suggestions around here somewhere, but it
seems to have been buried, I'll have to dig it out and let you all
know about them.

Cya's,
David Storey
